{"tid":714102,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國接管澳洲10個廣播頻率　美媒：中國正贏得太平洋","createTime":"2018-06-23T11:44:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-24T09:14:41.000Z","uid":141151,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"91cdb02c2084ba0aae0099312f24e4efa013232f","tid":714102,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T11:44:44.000Z","msg":"中國接管澳洲10個廣播頻率　美媒：中國正贏得太平洋<br />\n<br />\n據澳洲媒體報導，曾經被澳洲廣播電台（ABC）使用過的多達10個頻率，如今將用來播出中國國際廣播電台的節目，包括可以被瓦努阿圖、斐濟、薩摩亞等國接收的電台頻率。<br />\n<br />\n有澳洲媒體對中國影響力上升表示擔憂。另有美國媒體指，中國接管南太平洋廣播表明北京正贏得太平洋地區。<br />\n<br />\n由於目前只服務於有限的聽眾，且已經出現新的提供內容方式，ABC去年決定結束國際短波服務，其中包括面向巴布亞新幾內亞和太平洋地區的播音。<br />\n<br />\n不過，這一空缺迅速被補上。<span style=\"color: red;\">澳洲技術專家彼得&middot;馬克告訴ABC：「由於澳洲廣播電台已經取消短波，我們過去使用的許多頻率現在已被中國針對亞太地區的電台接管。」而澳洲廣播電台的前傳輸經理奈吉爾&middot;霍姆斯（Nigel Holmes）則告訴《澳洲人報》，兩個前澳洲廣播電台波段現在播出中國廣播電台針對澳洲的節目。</span><br />\n<br />\n因為警惕中國影響，ABC的舉動遭到澳洲媒體圈、政界和學界批評。《澳洲人報》就說，中國在南太地區日益增強的軟實力競爭中再下一城。<br />\n<br />\n《澳洲人報》還引述澳國家党副領袖布裡齊特&middot;加勒特（Bridget McKenzie）去年的話說，結束短波播音的做法令人「深深擔憂」。<br />\n<br />\n而<span style=\"color: red;\">美國《商業內幕》則稱，中國接管了澳洲放棄的廣播，這表明北京正贏得太平洋地區。這種情況表明，西方國家在外交、基礎設施建設及救援方面會留下真空，中國能夠輕易填補這一空白。</span><br />\n<br />\n（多維新聞）"},{"pid":"0de0a1ca615c68fe20a80cb5b14dd2cf90f2cb11","tid":714102,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T11:55:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8275919d3c25ed8a5911f856f04bc9b2d8c9e9f2","tid":714102,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T11:57:31.000Z","msg":"中國或成最大贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc91ada4dfae6d48c9aac5f5c1365bb1becd4de9","tid":714102,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T11:58:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b94e4c776d714e4891fa07c22a9fe2d43ada616c","tid":714102,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T12:43:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e88d7237dd83def8c5806199c87fc3edb2128efb","tid":714102,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8275919d3c25ed8a5911f856f04bc9b2d8c9e9f2","tid":714102,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T11:57:31.000Z","msg":"中國或成最大贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T13:04:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52d5cdb6313b5011666fa90e2575584defe1da0c","tid":714102,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T13:12:58.000Z","msg":"贏夠未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2e625722ceee16b21e7893e9065c230e0ebe732","tid":714102,"uid":59898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T13:18:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/red.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f979571567c66dd97225086f00e74dd79781f62","tid":714102,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"52d5cdb6313b5011666fa90e2575584defe1da0c","tid":714102,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T13:12:58.000Z","msg":"贏夠未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T07:33:11.000Z","msg":"未<br />\n贏埋大西洋北冰洋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5d85130d44a3bb73f5c125156fbf1011cb58bb7","tid":714102,"uid":57376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T09:14:41.000Z","msg":"繼續啦，繼續做多啲陰濕野啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你唔做啲歐豬美豬點會發覺燒到埋身<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n遲早迫到人地又一次八國聯軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}